{{Infobox language |name = Guya |altname = Guiarak |states = [[Papua New Guinea]] |region = [[Madang Province]] |ethnicity = |speakers = 130 |date = 1981 |ref = e18 |familycolor = Papuan |fam1 = [[Trans–New Guinea languages|Trans–New Guinea]] |fam2 = [[Finisterre–Huon languages|Finisterre–Huon]] |fam3 = [[Finisterre languages|Finisterre]] |fam4 = [[Warup languages|Warup]] |iso3 = gka |glotto=guya1251 |glottorefname=Guya }} '''Guya''' (Guiarak) is one of the [[Finisterre languages]] of [[Papua New Guinea]].
